      "content": "\"endure the sinking\"... i don't know. that sounds so exhausting. what's the point of just sitting there waiting for the water to get me? if the ship is definitely going down, isn't it more logical to just leave before the crash? it feels like people are just clinging to life out of habit, but there doesn't seem to be any actual logic in staying for the worst part.",
